      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. The engine has significant mechanical issues and does not currently start, and the transmission requires a complete overhaul. The exterior shows extensive wear, including deep scratches, several dents, and noticeable rust on the frame and lower body panels. Inside, the cabin has seen better days, with torn upholstery and non-functional electronic components. This car is being sold strictly 'as-is' and would be most suitable as a major restoration project or as a source for salvageable parts; it will need to be towed from the lot.",
